  "simulated.ponder.optical_sensor.text_5": "当应用过滤器时……",
  "simulated.ponder.optical_sensor.text_6": "……只有匹配的方块才会发出信号",
  "simulated.ponder.physics_assembler_block_properties.header": "方块的物理属性",
  "simulated.ponder.physics_assembler_block_properties.text_1": "有些方块可能有不同的重量……",
  "simulated.ponder.physics_assembler_block_properties.text_2": "轻",
  "simulated.ponder.physics_assembler_block_properties.text_3": "超重",
  "simulated.ponder.physics_assembler_block_properties.text_4": "……或其他特殊属性",
  "simulated.ponder.physics_assembler_block_properties.text_5": "光滑",
  "simulated.ponder.physics_assembler_block_properties.text_6": "易碎",
  "simulated.ponder.physics_assembler_intro.header": "组装模拟装置",
